What is this?
=============

This is a document attempts to collect a set of requirements for a global registry of
attribute types for use in claims-based protocols. It is provided in the Internet Draft
format.

Who is doing this?
==================

This work was inspired by a discussion in the ISOC identity ecosystem workshops in 
Amsterdam and Washington DC. Primary stuckees with trying to capture requirements
are Leif Johansson (NORDUnet), Heather Flanagan (ISOC) and James Clark (OASIS).
